            Abdoul ISSA BIDA
          
          
            
              I am a rookie fullstack Developer in the Dijon Area, France. I am graduated from University of Burgundy, France with a Master Degree in Databases & Artificial Intelligence. Currently I work in the developers Team at Actualis. I love talking about Data Science, Data Wrangling, analyzing and visualizing. I am also interested about Forecasting,Data Modeling, Tennis, Basketball and Foods (particulary Empanadas, Pastries & Desserts).
